&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://adityatelange.github.io/hugo-PaperMod/posts/papermod/papermod-faq/#bundling-custom-css-with-themes-assets"&gt;PaperMod - FAQs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
